name: FutaVeiny
description:
Disclaimer: I didn't create this LoRA. This LoRA was originally hosted over on MEGA.nz, but since most (if not all?) Colabs don't support MEGA links, I thought I'd post it here so people who only use Google Colab could try it too.

This is a Futanari LoRA. All the examples you see above have been generated using AbyssOrangeMix3 (AOM3). Feel free to experiment with other models. Here are the author's notes:

  • Requires "veiny penis" in prompts.

  • Works best at around weight 1.0, CFG 7.0.

  • I used DPM++ 2M Karras, 15 steps in all testing, but more steps are recommended for actual generations. (20-30)

  • Recommended hi-res upscaler is R-ESRGAN 4x+ (Some of the examples I've posted have been upscaled with Latent Nearest-Exact), but feel free to experiment.

  • Not extensively tested for multiple subjects, hardcore sex, etc

Please leave a review with your results if you like the LoRA. Enjoy!
